<div class="centered-container">
	<h3>
		<span style="font-size:20px;"><em><strong>Biography</strong></em></span></h3>
	<p style="font-size:16px;">
		I am an Associate Professor at the Chinese University of Hong Kong (CUHK). I received my B.E. in Software Engineering in 2011 from Fudan University and PhD in Computer Science in 2016 from Nanyang Technological University, Singapore.</p>
	<hr />
	<h3>
		<span style="font-size:20px;"><em>Research Interest</em></span></h3>
	<p style="font-size:16px;">
		Database, data mining and machine learning, with a special interest in big data processing and analytics. Current topics include:</p>
	<ul style="font-size:16px;">
		<li>
			Sampling-based approximation algorithm design;</li>
		<li>
			Effective index design;</li>
		<li>
			Efficient dynamic data processing;</li>
		<li>
			Large data analysis, especially large-scale graph data analysis.</li>
	</ul>
	<hr />
	<h3>
		<span style="font-size:24px;"><em>Hiring</em></span></h3>
	<p style="font-size:16px;">
		I am looking for self-motivated <u><strong><em>research assistants, PhD and postdocs</em></strong></u>. For interested applicants, please send me a detailed transcript (of the applicant&#39;s undergraduate study and postgraduate study if applicable) and a CV that lists the applicant&#39;s awards (since high school) and publications.</p>
	<hr />
